    <entry>
      <title>STL与部分排序算法</title>
      <link href="/2026/03/04/2025_11_20/"/>
      <url>/2026/03/04/2025_11_20/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="C-STL"><a href="#C-STL" class="headerlink" title="C++ STL"></a>C++ STL</h2><h3 id="什么是STL🧐"><a href="#什么是STL🧐" class="headerlink" title="什么是STL🧐"></a>什么是STL🧐</h3><p>STL即标准模板库（Standard Template Library），是C++标准库的一部分，提供了很多可直接使用的数据结构和算法。一般算法竞赛都支持STL库的使用，合理使用STL可以避免大量的造轮子工作，提高效率。</p><h3 id="STL容器"><a href="#STL容器" class="headerlink" title="STL容器"></a>STL容器</h3><h4 id="迭代器"><a href="#迭代器" class="headerlink" title="迭代器"></a>迭代器</h4><p>迭代器用于访问STL容器中的元素（类似指针<br><code>#include&lt;iterator&gt;</code><br><strong>常用运算符</strong></p><ul><li>自增++自减—迭代器前后移动1位</li><li>+或-整型前后移动指定位数</li><li>解引用*用于获取或修改它指向的元素</li><li>头迭代器begin()可以获得容器第一个元素的迭代器</li><li>尾迭代器end()可以获得指向容器尾端的迭代器（“尾端”不是最后一个元素，可以视为最后一个元素的后继）<br>示例：使用迭代器遍历vector<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;::iterator it = a.<span class="built_in">begin</span>();it!=a.<span class="built_in">end</span>();it++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout&lt;&lt;*it&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>使用auto关键字简化迭代器类型<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">auto</span> it = a.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(); it != a.<span class="built_in">end</span>(); it++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; *it &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>C++11之后支持<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> num : a)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout&lt;&lt;num&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="vector"><a href="#vector" class="headerlink" title="vector"></a>vector</h4></li><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;vector&gt;</code></li><li>构造函数<code>vector&lt;int&gt; a(n,m)</code>创建一个元素类型为<code>int</code>，大小为<code>n</code>，元素初值为<code>m</code>的一维数组<code>a</code>（时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script>，和数组大小成线性关系)</li><li>访问元素（时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）<ul><li><code>v.at(pos)</code>返回下标为<code>pos</code>的引用</li><li><code>v[pos]</code>返回下标为<code>pos</code>的引用</li><li><code>v.front() v.back()</code>返回首元素、尾元素的引用</li></ul></li><li>获取数组大小<code>a.size()</code></li><li>重新分配数组大小<code>a.resize()</code></li><li>末尾添加新元素<code>a.push_back(m)</code><ul><li>平均时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script></li><li>最坏时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(N)</script>（若超出当前分配内存的大小则重新分配内存并复制已有数据）</li></ul></li><li>删除末尾元素<code>a.pop_back()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>判断数组是否为空<code>a.empty()</code>返回<code>bool</code>类型</li><li>清空数组<code>a.clear()</code><h4 id="stack"><a href="#stack" class="headerlink" title="stack"></a>stack</h4>栈（先进后出）</li><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;stack&gt;</code></li><li>创建一个栈<code>stack&lt;int&gt; s</code></li><li>访问栈顶元素<code>s.top()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>进栈<code>s.push(data)</code>元素压入栈顶（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>出栈<code>s.pop()</code>栈顶元素出栈（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>获取大小<code>s.size()</code></li><li>判空<code>s.empty()</code><h4 id="queue"><a href="#queue" class="headerlink" title="queue"></a>queue</h4>队列（先进先出）</li><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;queue&gt;</code></li><li>创建队列<code>queue&lt;int&gt;q</code></li><li>访问队首<code>q.front()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）   </li><li>访问队尾<code>q.end()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>入队<code>q.push(data)</code>元素压入队尾（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>出队<code>q.pop()</code>队首元素出队（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>获取大小<code>q.size()</code></li><li>判空<code>q.empty()</code><h4 id="deque"><a href="#deque" class="headerlink" title="deque"></a>deque</h4>双端队列（两端都可以出队入队）</li><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;deque&gt;</code></li><li>创建<code>deque&lt;int&gt;de</code>（时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script>，和容器大小成线性关系)</li><li>访问：<code>de.front() de.back()</code>返回队首\队尾元素的引用 （时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>出队：队尾元素出队<code>de.pop_back()</code> 队首元素出队<code>de.pop_front()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>入队：压入队首<code>de.push_front()</code> 压入队尾<code>de.push_back()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>获取大小<code>de.size()</code></li><li>判空<code>de.empty()</code><h4 id="priority-queue"><a href="#priority-queue" class="headerlink" title="priority_queue"></a>priority_queue</h4>优先队列（默认为大顶堆，即队列顶部为最大的元素）：按照元素的优先级进行排序，（默认）每次出队操作总是弹出优先级最高的元素</li><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;priority_queue&gt;</code></li><li>创建<code>priority_queue&lt;int&gt;pq</code>默认为大顶堆<ul><li>提供比较函数实现自定义类型的优先队列<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">cmp</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">operator</span><span class="params">()</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a, <span class="type">int</span> b)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a &gt; b;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">priority_queue&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;, cmp&gt; pq2;<span class="comment">//小顶堆</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//元素为pair类型，且以pair中的second从小到大排序</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">cmp2</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">operator</span><span class="params">()</span><span class="params">(pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="type">int</span>&gt; a, pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="type">int</span>&gt; b)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">        </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> a.second &gt; b.second;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    priority_queue&lt;pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;, vector&lt;pair&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>插入<code>pq.push(val)</code>将元素<code>val</code>插入优先队列并重新调整堆以保证优先级顺序，时间复杂度近似为<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script></li><li><code>pq.pop()</code>移除队列顶部的元素（即移除优先级最高的元素），时间复杂度近似为<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script></li><li>访问队列顶部元素<code>pq.top()</code> 返回优先级最高的元素的引用，（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>获取大小<code>pq.size()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）</li><li>判空<code>pq.empty()</code>（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script>）<h4 id="set"><a href="#set" class="headerlink" title="set"></a>set</h4></li></ul><ul><li><code>set</code>、<code>multiset</code>和<code>map</code>通常采用红黑树实现，其插入、查看和删除操作的时间复杂度近似为<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script><br>类似数学中的集合，set中不会出现值相同的元素，默认从小到大排序</li></ul><ul><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;set&gt;</code></li><li>创建<code>set&lt;int&gt;s</code></li><li>插入<code>s.insert(x)</code></li><li>删除（时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script>）<ul><li><code>erase(x)</code>删除值为x的所有元素，返回删除元素的个数</li><li><code>erase(pos)</code>删除迭代器为pos的元素</li><li><code>erase(first,last)</code>删除迭代器在<script type="math/tex">[first,last)</script>范围内的所有元素</li></ul></li><li>获取大小<code>s.size()</code></li><li>清空<code>s.clear()</code></li><li>查找<ul><li><code>count(x)</code>返回set内键为x的元素数量</li><li><code>find(x)</code>返回set内键为x的元素的迭代器，若不存在该元素则返回end()</li><li><code>lower_bound(x)</code>返回指向首个不小于x的元素的迭代器，若不存在则返回end()</li><li><code>upper_bound(x)</code>返回指向首个大于x的元素的迭代器，若不存在则返回end()</li></ul></li><li>判空<code>s.empty()</code></li><li>自定义比较方式<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">cmp</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">operator</span><span class="params">()</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a, <span class="type">int</span> b)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a &gt; b;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">set&lt;<span class="type">int</span>,  cmp&gt; s;<span class="comment">//从大到小排列</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="multiset"><a href="#multiset" class="headerlink" title="multiset"></a>multiset</h4></li></ul><p>与set类似，但multiset允许出现值相同的元素</p><h4 id="map"><a href="#map" class="headerlink" title="map"></a>map</h4><p>关联式容器<br>有序键值对容器，map内不会出现键相同的元素，元素默认按照键从小到大排序</p><ul><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;map&gt;</code></li><li>创建<code>map&lt;string,int&gt; m</code>创建一个键为<code>string</code>类型，值为<code>int</code>类型的map</li><li>插入<code>m[key] = value</code></li><li>查询<ul><li><code>value = m[key]</code>获取键为key的值</li><li><code>count(x)</code></li><li><code>find(x)</code>返回键为x的元素的迭代器，若不存在则返回<code>end()</code></li><li><code>lower_bound(x)</code>返回指向首个键不小于x的元素的迭代器，若不存在则返回<code>end()</code></li><li><code>upper_bound(x)</code>返回指向首个键大于x的元素的迭代器，若不存在则返回<code>end()</code></li></ul></li><li>遍历<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (map&lt;string, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;::iterator it = m.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(); it != m.<span class="built_in">end</span>(); it++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; it-&gt;first &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; it-&gt;second &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//C++11之后</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">auto</span> &amp;p : m)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; p.first &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; p.second &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">auto</span> it = m.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(); it != m.<span class="built_in">end</span>(); it++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; it-&gt;first &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; it-&gt;second &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>删除<br><code>m.erase(key)</code>删除键为key的所有元素<br><code>m.erase(pos)</code>删除迭代器为pos的元素<br><code>m.erase(first,last)</code>删除迭代器在<script type="math/tex">[first,last)</script>范围内的所有元素</li><li>清空<code>m.clear()</code></li><li>获取大小<code>m.size()</code></li><li>判空<code>m.empty()</code></li><li>自定义比较方式<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">cmp</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">operator</span><span class="params">()</span><span class="params">(string a, string b)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a &gt; b;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">map&lt;string,<span class="type">int</span>,cmp&gt; m;<span class="comment">//从大到小排列</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="string"><a href="#string" class="headerlink" title="string"></a>string</h4></li><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;string&gt;</code></li><li>构造<code>string s</code>创建一个空字符串s</li><li>初始化<code>string s(10,&#39;0&#39;)</code>创建一个长度为10每个字符都为0的字符串</li><li>赋值：用=赋值<code>string s = &quot;hello world!&quot;</code></li><li>读入<code>cin&gt;&gt;s</code>输出<code>cout&lt;&lt;s</code></li><li>字符串拼接<code>s = s1 + s2</code>，时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script>（n为拼接后字符串的长度）</li><li>获取字符串长度<code>s.length()</code>，时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script></li><li>截取字符串<code>s1 = s.substr(n,m)</code>从下标为n的字符开始截取m个字符，若m缺省则截取下标为n及其后面的所有字符，时间复杂度为<script type="math/tex">O(m)</script></li><li>插入字符串，时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n + m)</script><ul><li><code>s.insert(index,n,ch)</code>在<code>index</code>处连续插入n次字符串ch</li><li><code>s.insert(index,str)</code>在<code>index</code>处插入字符串str</li></ul></li><li>删除字符串<code>s.erase(index,n)</code>删除从下标为<code>index</code>开始（包含）的n个字符，若n缺省则删去index及其后面的所有字符，时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script></li><li>查找<code>s.find(str,pos)</code>查找字符串s中在pos之后（包含）第一次出现str子串的位置（子串第一个元素的位置），若不存在则返回<code>string::npos</code><br>*<code>s.find(str,pos)</code>时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(nm)</script>，n为字符串总长，m为查询子串的长度，相当于暴力查询，不建议用<code>find()</code>解决时间复杂度要求较高的问题</li><li>替换字符串<code>s.replace(n,m,str)</code>将从下标为n开始的m个字符的子串替换为str，时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script><h4 id="pair"><a href="#pair" class="headerlink" title="pair"></a>pair</h4>用于将两个变量关联在一起</li><li>头文件<code>#include&lt;pair&gt;</code></li><li>初始化<ul><li>定义时初始化<code>pair&lt;int,double&gt; p(1,0.1)</code></li><li>先定义后赋值<code>pair&lt;int,double&gt;p1;  p1.first = 1;  p1.second = 0.1</code></li><li>使用<code>make_pair</code>函数<code>pair&lt;int,double&gt;p2 = make_pair(1,0.1)</code></li></ul></li><li><code>first</code>与<code>second</code>用于访问pair包含的两个变量</li><li>大小比较<code>&lt;,&gt;,&lt;=,&gt;=</code>:会优先比较两个pair中的第一个变量，第一个变量若相等再比较第二个变量</li><li>与其他容器组合使用<code>vector&lt;pair&lt;int,int&gt;&gt;</code><h3 id="STL算法"><a href="#STL算法" class="headerlink" title="STL算法"></a>STL算法</h3>STL提供了很多实现算法的模板函数，基本都包含在<code>&lt;algorithm&gt;</code>头文件中。</li><li><strong>find</strong>： <code>find(v.begin(),v.end(),value)</code>顺序查找值为value的元素</li><li><strong>swap</strong>：交换两个变量的值<code>swap(a,b)</code></li><li><strong>reverse</strong>：翻转数组、字符串,时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script><ul><li><code>reverse(v.begin(),v.end())</code>反转整个容器</li><li><code>reverse(v.begin() + 1, v.begin() + 3)</code>对容器下标<script type="math/tex">[1,3)</script>部分进行反转</li></ul></li><li><strong>sort</strong>：排序，默认将元素从小到大排序，也可以通过自定义比较函数cmp实现复杂比较,时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n log n)</script><ul><li><code>sort(v.begin(),v.end(),cmp)</code>对整个容器排序</li><li><code>sort(v.begin() + 1, v.begin() + 3, cmp)</code>对容器下标<script type="math/tex">[1,3)</script>部分进行排序</li></ul></li><li><strong>merge</strong><br>将两个有序区间有序合并到第三个序列的迭代器上<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;v1 = &#123;<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">5</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;v2 = &#123;<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">6</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;<span class="built_in">res</span>(<span class="number">6</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">merge</span>(v<span class="number">1.</span><span class="built_in">begin</span>(),v<span class="number">1.</span><span class="built_in">end</span>(),v<span class="number">2.</span><span class="built_in">begin</span>(),v<span class="number">2.</span><span class="built_in">end</span>(),res.<span class="built_in">begin</span>());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><ul><li><strong>max和min</strong>：<code>max(a,b)</code><br>求多个元素的最大值或最小值：<code>max(a,max(b,c))</code>对于c++11之后<code>max(&#123;a,b,c&#125;</code>)<h2 id="常见排序算法"><a href="#常见排序算法" class="headerlink" title="常见排序算法"></a>常见排序算法</h2><h3 id="冒泡排序"><a href="#冒泡排序" class="headerlink" title="冒泡排序"></a>冒泡排序</h3>算法步骤（升序排序为例）<br>1.从第一个元素开始，比较相邻的两个元素，若前一个元素更大，则交换两个元素；<br>2.对每一对相邻元素重复上述步骤，直到容器末尾。此时最大的元素已被冒泡到容器末尾<br>3.忽略已排序的最后一个元素，重复上述步骤，直至排序完成</li></ul><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; v = &#123;<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; v.<span class="built_in">size</span>(); i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; v.<span class="built_in">size</span>() - i - <span class="number">1</span>; j++)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (v[j] &gt; v[j + <span class="number">1</span>])</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">swap</span>(v[j], v[j + <span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n^2)</script> （两层for循环遍历数组）对于大规模数据效率较低<br>空间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script> (原地排序不需要额外的存储）</p><h3 id="选择排序"><a href="#选择排序" class="headerlink" title="选择排序"></a>选择排序</h3><p>算法步骤（升序排序为例）<br>1.将容器分为已排序部分和未排序部分（初始时已排序部分为空）<br>2.在未排序部分中找到最小的元素，与未排序部分的第一个元素交换位置<br>3.将未排序部分的起始位置向后移动一位，扩大已排序部分的范围<br>4.重复上述步骤直至未排序部分为空</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">selectionSort</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp;arr, <span class="type">int</span> n)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> i, j, minn;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n - <span class="number">1</span>; i++)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        minn = i;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (j = i + <span class="number">1</span>; j &lt; n; j++)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (arr[j] &lt; arr[minn])</span><br><span class="line">                minn= j;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">swap</span>(arr[minn], arr[i]);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n^2)</script>（两层for循环遍历数组）对于大规模数据效率较低<br>空间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script> (原地排序不需要额外的存储）</p><h3 id="插入排序"><a href="#插入排序" class="headerlink" title="插入排序"></a>插入排序</h3><p>算法步骤（升序排序为例）<br>1.将容器分为已排序部分和未排序部分（初始时已排序部分只包含第一个元素）<br>2.在未排序部分中取出第一个元素，将该元素与已排序部分从后往前依次比较，找到合适的位置插入<br>3.重复上述步骤直至未排序部分为空</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">insertionSort</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp;arr, <span class="type">int</span> n)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> i, j, key;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt; n; i++)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        key = arr[i];</span><br><span class="line">        j = i - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (j &gt;= <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; arr[j] &gt; key)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            arr[j + <span class="number">1</span>] = arr[j];</span><br><span class="line">            j = j - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        arr[j + <span class="number">1</span>] = key;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>时间复杂度：<br>最坏<script type="math/tex">O(n^2)</script>原列表完全逆序，每次插入都需要移动所有已排序的元素<br>最好<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script>原列表有序，只需遍历一次列表<br>空间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(1)</script> (原地排序不需要额外的存储）</p><h3 id="归并排序"><a href="#归并排序" class="headerlink" title="归并排序"></a>归并排序</h3><p>算法步骤（升序排序为例）<br>1.将容器对半分为两个子数组<br>2.递归地对每个子数组进行排序<br>3.将两个已排序的子数组合并为一个有序数组<br>合并操作<br>1.申请空间存放待合并的数组<br>2.设定两个指针，最初分别指向两个待合并数组的起始位置<br>3.比较两个指针所指向的元素，选择较小的放入原数组，并移动指针到下一位置<br>4.重复步骤3直至某一指针到达数组末尾<br>5.将未到达末尾的数组的剩余元素复制到原数组</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">merge</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; &amp;arr, <span class="type">int</span> start, <span class="type">int</span> mid, <span class="type">int</span> end)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> l = <span class="number">0</span>, r = <span class="number">0</span>, k = start;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">left</span><span class="params">(arr.begin() + start, arr.begin() + mid + <span class="number">1</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">right</span><span class="params">(arr.begin() + mid + <span class="number">1</span>, arr.begin() + end + <span class="number">1</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (l &lt; left.<span class="built_in">size</span>() &amp;&amp; r &lt; right.<span class="built_in">size</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (left[l] &lt;= right[r])</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            arr[k] = left[l];</span><br><span class="line">            l++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            arr[k] = right[r];</span><br><span class="line">            r++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        k++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//复制剩余元素</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(l&lt;left.<span class="built_in">size</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        arr[k] = left[l];</span><br><span class="line">        l++;</span><br><span class="line">        k++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(r&lt;right.<span class="built_in">size</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        arr[k] = right[r];</span><br><span class="line">        r++;</span><br><span class="line">        k++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">mergeSort</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; &amp;arr, <span class="type">int</span> start, <span class="type">int</span> end)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (start &gt;= end)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> mid = (start + end) / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">mergeSort</span>(arr, start, mid);<span class="comment">//递归地处理左右子数组</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">mergeSort</span>(arr, mid + <span class="number">1</span>, end);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">merge</span>(arr, start, mid, end);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//调用mergeSort(arr, 0, n - 1);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n log n)</script><br>分解：每次对半分，需要执行<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script>次<br>合并：<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script><br>空间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script>（合并操作需要额外空间来存储）</p><h3 id="快速排序"><a href="#快速排序" class="headerlink" title="快速排序"></a>快速排序</h3><p>算法步骤（升序排序为例）<br>1.选择一个元素作为基准<br>2.将所有小于基准元素的元素放在基准的左侧，所有大于基准元素的元素都放在基准的右侧<br>3.递归地对基准元素左侧和右侧的子数组进行快速排序</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">quicksort</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; &amp;arr, <span class="type">int</span> left, <span class="type">int</span> right)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (left &gt;= right)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> i = left, j = right + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> key = arr[left];<span class="comment">//选取第一个元素作为基准</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (i &lt; j)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (++i &lt;= right &amp;&amp; arr[i] &lt; key)</span><br><span class="line">            ;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (--j &gt; left &amp;&amp; arr[j] &gt; key)</span><br><span class="line">            ;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (i &gt;= j)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">swap</span>(arr[i], arr[j]);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">swap</span>(arr[left], arr[j]);<span class="comment">//放置基准元素</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">quicksort</span>(arr, left, j - <span class="number">1</span>);<span class="comment">//递归处理左右子数组</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">quicksort</span>(arr, j + <span class="number">1</span>, right);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>时间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n log n)</script><br>分解：每次对半分，需要执行<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script>次<br>合并：<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script><br>空间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script>（原地排序，递归调用函数需要额外<script type="math/tex">O(log n)</script>的空间）</p><h3 id="希尔排序"><a href="#希尔排序" class="headerlink" title="希尔排序"></a>希尔排序</h3><p>对普通插入排序的优化<br>算法步骤（升序排序为例）<br>1.选择一个增量序列（常用<code>n/2,n/4,...1</code>)，用于将数组分成若干子数组<br>2.按照增量序列分组后，对每个子列表进行插入排序<br>3.逐步缩小增量，重复上述步骤直到增量为1<br>4.当增量为1时，对整个数组进行一次插入排序<br>示例：<br>初始数组 8，7，6，5，4，3，2，1<br>增量为4，分成4个子数组8,4；7,3；6,2；5,1各自插入排序后4,8 ; 3,7 ; 2,6 ; 1,5<br>此时数组为4,3,2,1,8,7,6,5<br>增量取2，分为4,2,8,6和3,1,7,5各自排序后2,4,6,8和1,3,5,7<br>此时2,1,4,3,6,5,8,7<br>增量为1，进行一次插入排序后得到有序序列1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">shellSort</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; &amp;arr, <span class="type">int</span> len)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> gap = len / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (gap &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;    <span class="comment">//对每个子列表进行插入排序</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = gap; i &lt; len; i++)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> temp = arr[i];<span class="comment">//当前待插入元素</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> j;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (j = i; j &gt;= gap &amp;&amp; arr[j - gap] &gt; temp; j -= gap)<span class="comment">//在子列表中找到合适的位置插入</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                arr[j] = arr[j - gap];</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            arr[j] = temp;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        gap /= <span class="number">2</span>;<span class="comment">//减小增量</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>时间复杂度取决于增量序列的选择，平均在<script type="math/tex">O(n log n)</script>到<script type="math/tex">O(n^2)</script>之间<br>空间复杂度<script type="math/tex">O(n)</script>（合并操作需要额外空间来存储）<br>更多</p><ul><li>更多关于STL<br>C++ 标准库简介 - OI Wiki<br>C++ STL 教程 | 菜鸟教程</li><li>更多关于排序算法<br>排序简介 - OI Wiki<br>1.0 十大经典排序算法 | 菜鸟教程</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
